## Conventions

- `ChangeNotifier` for simple, local state
- `Riverpod` or `Provider` for dependency injection
- `BLoC` for complex event-driven flows
- Never access state directly, always via getters
- `notifyListeners` only after real mutation
- Separate notifiers by domain (auth, cart, profile)
